      "slug": "modulo-06-armazenamento-05-fsx",
      "title": "Amazon FSx — sistemas de arquivos gerenciados (Windows, Lustre)",
      "module": "modulo-06-armazenamento",
      "moduleLabel": "Storage",
      "relative": "modulo-06-armazenamento/05-fsx.md",
